Chief Executive Officer
Offshore Recruitment Services
UAE
Posted on: 29 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Our client, an international interiors company, are looking for a CEO to direct and steer business performance in the region.
The ideal candidate will have a background in interior fit-out, with a minimum of eight years at a senior management level. The role requires a high level of commercial, cultural and financial awareness, with the ability to think creatively and laterally over a wide range of complex issues. Excellent communication and leadership skills at all levels are a must.
REQUIREMENTS
In addition, you must possess strong interpersonal and negotiation skills, be decisive enough to make tough decisions in the interest of the business, have a clear understanding of financial, marketing and operational responsibilities and be able to work well under pressure.
If you have all the skills and experience required please apply online.
Due to high volume of received applications, we are unable to respond to each application on individual basis therefore only successful candidates will be contacted.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Offshore Recruitment Services specialise in the recruitment of in all aspects of offshore vacancies for all levels of permanent, temporary and contract positions.
Whether a client is searching for a highly skilled candidate, looking to head hunt a specific individual, a team of contractors for a project or management of gifted personnel, we are ready and have a proven track record of meeting such requirements.
Offshore Recruitment Services was formed with the specific aim of providing a quality service to link key candidates to our clients. We find the right people for your business.
